entries.name: count
entries.desc: The count of items is never updated for the silent progress reporter.

entries.name: new(out_stream, size, initial_message, terminal_message = nil)
entries.desc: Creates a silent progress reporter that ignores all input arguments.

entries.name: done()
entries.desc: Does not print anything when complete as this object has taken a vow of silence.

entries.name: updated(message)
entries.desc: Does not print message when updated as this object has taken a vow of silence.
